Joyce Watson, as Administratrix of the Estate of Albert K. Watson, Deceased, Appellant, v Jamaica Hospital et al., Respondents, et al., Defendants. Submitted February 22, 1977; decided April 7, 1977

Reported below, 54 AD2d 695.

Motions by respondents (a) Jamaica Hospital and (b) Marzulli and Smith to dismiss the appeal herein granted and the appeal dismissed, without costs, upon the ground that the order appealed from involves the ex;ercise of discretion of the type not reviewable by the Court of Appeals.
